C.val:
Below is a selector of various samples of XSLT 4.0, whose stylesheet can be
                     loaded into the Code textarea and edited if required.

For the samples
                     there are one or more example inputs in XML format, that can similarly be
                     loaded into the Input textarea.

The run button processes the transform,
                     with input as the source document, by conversion to an equivalent XSLT 3.0
                     stylesheet and evaluation via the

conversion of XPath 4.0 expressions into
                     XPath 3.1. As everything is

experimental, not all current syntax,
                     semantics and functions are implemented fully or correctly.

as the top-level program and an XSLT4 → XSLT3 conversion stylesheet.
                     There is

server-side processing, apart from initial delivery of
                     necessary files.
